{"id":97870,"type":6,"name":"Fairly Legal Season 2","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/0a/43/97870_D6dnT.jpg","summary":"　　本剧讲述顶级诉讼律师Kate Reed（Sarah Shahi）在工作中长期目睹官僚主义和不公正的判决结果，对律师这个职业产生了强烈反感。她决定改行当法律调解人，专门与律师为敌（当事双方如果同意调解，就没有官司，没有官司就不需要律师）。 Kate利用自己丰富的法律知识和女性特有的直觉，再加上天不怕地不怕的性格，成功介入了许多惹人瞩目的矛盾冲突－－既有世界500强企业的大官司，也有因感情问题而闹离婚的父亲去世后，Kate一直与继母（Virginia Williams）不合，可继母偏偏是她的老板……与此同时，她与在地区检察官办公室当律师的前夫（Michael Trucco）依然藕断丝连－－当不成夫妻不要紧，至少还可以当「床伴」。还好Kate身边有一位好助手（Baron Vaughn），这位文雅的「书生」总是替她把一切都打点好，让她可以安安心心过完每一天。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>律政佳人 第二季</li><li><span>集数: </span>13</li><li><span>开始: </span>2012-03-16</li><li><span>结束: </span>2012-06-15</li><li><span>类型: </span>律政</li><li><span>国家/地区: </span>美国</li><li><span>语言: </span>英语</li><li><span>电视台: </span>USA Network</li>","collection":{"collect":1},"tags":[{"name":"剧情","count":1},{"name":"美剧","count":1}],"eps":[{"id":377405,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/377405","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":377406,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/377406","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":377407,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/377407","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":377408,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/377408","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":377409,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/377409","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":377410,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/377410","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":377411,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/377411","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":377412,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/377412","type":0,"sort":8,"name":"","nam